    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1936-07-23T18:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1936-07-23T18:00:00-05:00" n="592"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d592">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">852.00/2265f: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Consul at Barcelona</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Franklin</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1936-07-23T19:00:00-04:00"
                            >July 23, 1936—7 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Belgian Government has requested our cooperation in the evacuation of Belgian
                    nationals from Barcelona. The Commanding Officer of the <hi rend="italic"
                        >Exeter</hi> has been informed of this and we have also informed <pb
                        facs="0737" n="638" xml:id="pg_638"/> the Belgian Government that while
                    space on the vessel is limited, we will give every consideration to its
                    request.</p>
                <p>We assume that such Americans as avail themselves of the use of the <hi
                        rend="italic">Exeter</hi> will be sufficiently supplied with funds so as to
                    take care of themselves. We very much hope that this is the situation since we
                    have no particular funds available for this purpose. However, you should let us
                    know whether there are any destitute Americans in need of funds.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
